---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="The Omnirepo | Structure Your Organization for AI">
  <main class="min-h-screen">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative px-6 py-24 md:py-32 lg:py-40">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <p class="text-blue-400 font-mono text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">
          A Pattern for AI-Ready Organizations
        </p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6">
          THE <span class="text-blue-400">OMNIREPO</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">
          Your entire company.<br />
          One traversable structure.<br />
          AI as the connective tissue.
        </p>
        <a
          href="#starter-kit"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-400 text-white font-medium px-8 py-4 rounded-lg transition-colors"
        >
          Get the Free Starter Kit
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 3.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Problem Section -->
    <section class="px-6 py-20 bg-zinc-900/50">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">The Problem</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Your strategy lives in Notion. Code in GitHub. Marketing in Google Docs.
            Brand guidelines in a PDF no one reads. Operational knowledge in Slack threads.
          </p>
          <p>
            AI tools are capable. But they operate in silos.
            Your coding assistant doesn't know your brand voice.
            Your writing assistant doesn't know your product architecture.
          </p>
          <p class="text-zinc-200 font-medium">
            The problem isn't AI capability. It's organizational structure.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Manifesto Section -->
    <section class="px-6 py-24" id="manifesto">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 lg:p-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-12 text-center">
            THE OMNIREPO MANIFESTO
          </h2>
          <!-- Preamble -->
          <p class="text-zinc-400 text-lg text-center mb-12 leading-relaxed">
            Knowledge trapped in heads is lost. Coordination is exhausting.<br />
            Every alignment meeting is an hour stolen from creation.<br />
            <span class="text-zinc-200">Structure gives that time back.</span>
          </p>

          <div class="space-y-8">
            <div class="flex gap-6">
              <span class="text-blue-400 font-mono text-2xl font-bold shrink-0">1.</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">STRUCTURE OVER PROCESS</h3>
                <p class="text-zinc-400">Alignment comes from shared context, not meetings. If you're coordinating manually, your structure is broken.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-6">
              <span class="text-blue-400 font-mono text-2xl font-bold shrink-0">2.</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">EVERYTHING TRAVERSABLE</h3>
                <p class="text-zinc-400">If AI can't read it, it can't help with it. No knowledge locked in heads, Slack threads, or tools that don't export.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-6">
              <span class="text-blue-400 font-mono text-2xl font-bold shrink-0">3.</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">HISTORY PRESERVED</h3>
                <p class="text-zinc-400">Every change tracked. Evolution visible. AI understands not just what exists, but how it evolved and why.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-6">
              <span class="text-blue-400 font-mono text-2xl font-bold shrink-0">4.</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">SINGLE SOURCE OF TRUTH</h3>
                <p class="text-zinc-400">Each concept lives in one place. Everything else references it. Never duplicate. Always link.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-6">
              <span class="text-blue-400 font-mono text-2xl font-bold shrink-0">5.</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">CONTEXT AT EVERY BOUNDARY</h3>
                <p class="text-zinc-400">Each domain declares how it works. AI reads these declarations before acting. No implicit knowledge.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-6">
              <span class="text-blue-400 font-mono text-2xl font-bold shrink-0">6.</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">DESIGN FOR AI, NOT JUST HUMANS</h3>
                <p class="text-zinc-400">Humans navigate. AI traverses. Optimize for both. Clear file names, consistent patterns, explicit relationships.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-6">
              <span class="text-blue-400 font-mono text-2xl font-bold shrink-0">7.</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">ORCHESTRATION AT THE ROOT</h3>
                <p class="text-zinc-400">Cross-cutting workflows live at the top. One command, multiple domains, coordinated output.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-6">
              <span class="text-blue-400 font-mono text-2xl font-bold shrink-0">8.</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">COMPOUND OVER TIME</h3>
                <p class="text-zinc-400">Every document makes AI more capable. Structure is an investment. The returns accumulate.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-zinc-800 text-center flex justify-between items-center">
            <span class="text-zinc-600 font-mono text-xs">v1.0</span>
            <a href="/MANIFESTO.pdf" class="text-zinc-500 hover:text-zinc-400 font-mono text-sm transition-colors">
              Download PDF ↓
            </a>
            <span class="text-zinc-500 font-mono text-sm">www.omnirepo.org</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Two Models Section -->
    <section class="px-6 py-20 bg-zinc-900/50">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-center">Two Models</h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-center mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          The omnirepo pattern works with either approach. Choose based on your team's needs.
        </p>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <!-- True Monorepo -->
          <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-xl p-8">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="text-blue-400 font-mono">/</span>
              True Monorepo
            </h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-zinc-400">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                Single repository, directory-based structure
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                Simple permissions model
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                Best for startups and small teams
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                Atomic commits across domains
              </li>
            </ul>
            <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-zinc-950 rounded-lg font-mono text-sm text-zinc-500">
              <pre>company/
├── os/
├── marketing/
├── engineering/
└── CLAUDE.md</pre>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Meta-repo -->
          <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-xl p-8">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="text-blue-400 font-mono">@</span>
              Meta-repo (Repo of Repos)
            </h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-zinc-400">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                Root repo with git submodules
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                Granular per-submodule permissions
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                Best for enterprises and regulated industries
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-400 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                Independent version control per domain
              </li>
            </ul>
            <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-zinc-950 rounded-lg font-mono text-sm text-zinc-500">
              <pre>hq/
├── os/ (submodule)
├── marketing/ (submodule)
├── apps/ (submodule)
└── CLAUDE.md</pre>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Starter Kit CTA Section -->
    <section class="px-6 py-24" id="starter-kit">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">
          THE OMNIREPO STARTER KIT
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-zinc-400 mb-10">
          Everything you need to structure your organization for AI. Free.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 mb-10">
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-left max-w-md mx-auto mb-10">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-400 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
              <span>The Manifesto (printable PDF)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-400 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
              <span>CLAUDE.md templates for 5 domains</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-400 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
              <span>Example slash commands</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-400 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
              <span>"Is your org ready?" checklist with scoring</span>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <!-- Kit Email Form -->
          <div class="max-w-md mx-auto">
            <script async data-uid="593012b9d0" src="https://omnirepo.kit.com/593012b9d0/index.js"></script>
            <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm mt-4">No spam. Just resources that help.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="px-6 py-12 border-t border-zinc-800">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-3">
          The Omnirepo emerged from real-world experience building AI-first organizations.
        </p>
        <a href="https://www.goldsborough.io/the-omnirepo-ai-orchestration-across-enterprises/" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 transition-colors">
          Read the origin story →
        </a>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </main>
</Layout>
